{"tid":1431940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[向大台說不]三個大台絕對唔應該存在嘅理由","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:23:06.000Z","uid":294772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae928f42b65d2d4fd1f2214750a7c31ad408169","tid":1431940,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1. 冇大台起度綁手綁腳，手足先可以做到遍地開花。大台係冇可能同時支援到好多個地方，信大台不如信嗰區啲街坊好過。「兄弟爬山，各自努力」先係唯一出路。<br />\n<br />\n2. 呢兩個月勇武賴以成功嘅係超高嘅執行力同埋應變能力。大台嘅存在毫無意義，只會成為義士嘅負累同掣肘，令抗爭嘅效率大幅降低。<br />\n<br />\n3. 依家港共政府係咁吹風話邊個係大台嗰個係大台，正正就係想我地自亂陣腳去爭做大台，等大台出黎再一舉殲滅。政府依家已經係迷失方向，佢地唯一嘅希望就係等一個箭靶出現，而大台正正就係嗰個箭靶。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要成功嘅話，大台一定唔可以出現<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32514bf5d623c52f4fb0cc2d065145e045e7b3bc","tid":1431940,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"ca70c9c3ebf812ddc189fff7d201c2143329ead8","tid":1431940,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"3214e25408058c939b521925cb5136ea31a89335","tid":1431940,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"82c71239e7544c878d5e5b65ad87053ee1d2bd2e","tid":1431940,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"9241be4358b8b8493682a6503026a74ba5a27b99","tid":1431940,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"六<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf13989bd9d04dc36e33c3762aebb4dd83923a2","tid":1431940,"uid":294772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"